            style="padding: 1.5rem; background-color: #ffffff"
          >
            <p><strong>You‚Äôll need:</strong></p>
            <ul>
              <li>1 tsp matcha powder</li>
              <li>2 tbsp hot water</li>
              <li>3/4 cup milk of choice</li>
              <li>1‚Äì2 tsp sugar or syrup (optional)</li>
              <li>1/3 cup cooked tapioca pearls</li>
              <li>Ice cubes</li>
            </ul>

            <p><strong>Steps:</strong></p>
            <ol>
              <li>Cook tapioca pearls (per package instructions).</li>
              <li>Whisk matcha with hot water until frothy.</li>
              <li>Stir in milk and sweetener.</li>
              <li>Add pearls to a glass with ice.</li>
              <li>Pour matcha mixture over and serve with a wide straw.</li>
            </ol>

            <p><strong>‚è±Ô∏è Takes 15‚Äì20 minutes</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

